<br>
As far as tank stackabliity, CH chain single npc fights are what screwed that one.<br>
<br>
They need more fights where you should have to enguage multiple npcs at once. But, then that doesnt solve anything by itself, why not use the monk who is arleady there for damage since he can tank just as well and avoid better.<br>
<br>
But, if they fix mitigation too, now you need tanks for the extra npcs rather then just someone who was already there for damage anyway. If these extra tank adds dont have sick damage, now you can group 6 paladins, they can do a prexus rotation, and they probably wont need any heals from clerics.<br>
